Name: Hyacine
Desc: As the city-state in the clouds crumbles through time, the Twilight Courtyard opens its gates once more, bringing a glimmer of light to Evernight.\nYou, Physician Hyacinthia, Chrysos Heir who guards the Sky Coreflame, must inherit your ancestors' will and mend the torn fabric of dusk and dawn.\nMay the rainbow light pour down, dissolve all grudges, and bring the dawn back to this land.

1.Name: Cradle the Candle of Night
1.Desc: When Hyacine is in the "After Rain" state, additionally increases the Max HP of all ally targets by <unbreak>#1[i]%</unbreak>, and immediately restores HP equal to <unbreak>#2[i]%</unbreak> of Hyacine's Max HP after using an attack.

2.Name: Come Sit in My Courtyard
2.Desc: When any ally target's HP decreases, this unit's SPD increases by <unbreak>#1[i]%</unbreak> for <unbreak>#2[i]</unbreak> turn(s).

3.Name: Depart, Unto the Sun!
3.Desc: Ultimate Lv. +2, up to a maximum of Lv. <unbreak>15</unbreak>.\nBasic ATK Lv. +1, up to a maximum of Lv. <unbreak>10</unbreak>.\nMemosprite Skill Lv. +1, up to a maximum of Lv. <unbreak>10</unbreak>.

4.Name: Sunlit Amber, Yours to Keep
4.Desc: The "Tempestuous Halt" Trace is enhanced. For every <unbreak>#1[i]</unbreak> of SPD exceeded, additionally increases Hyacine and Little Ica's CRIT DMG by <unbreak>#2[i]%</unbreak>.

5.Name: Twilight Drapes the Tide
5.Desc: Skill Lv. +2, up to a maximum of Lv. <unbreak>15</unbreak>.\nTalent Lv. +2, up to a maximum of Lv. <unbreak>15</unbreak>.\nMemosprite Talent Lv. +1, up to a maximum of Lv. <unbreak>10</unbreak>.

6.Name: O Sky, Heed My Plea
6.Desc: Little Ica uses Memosprite Skill and changes the amount of Healing tally cleared to <unbreak>#1[i]%</unbreak>. When Little Ica is on the field, increases all ally targets' All-Type <u>RES PEN</u> by <unbreak>#2[i]%</unbreak>.

140901.Name: When Breeze Kisses Cirrus
140901.Desc: Deals Wind DMG equal to <color=#f29e38ff><unbreak>#1[i]%</unbreak></color> of Hyacine's Max HP to a designated enemy target.

140902.Name: Love Over the Rainbow
140902.Desc: <u>Summons memosprite</u> Little Ica, restores HP equal to <color=#f29e38ff><unbreak>#1[f1]%</unbreak></color> of Hyacine's Max HP plus <color=#f29e38ff><unbreak>#2[i]</unbreak></color> for all allies aside from Little Ica, and restores HP equal to <color=#f29e38ff><unbreak>#3[f1]%</unbreak></color> of Hyacine's Max HP plus <color=#f29e38ff><unbreak>#4[i]</unbreak></color> for Little Ica.

140903.Name: We Who Fly <unbreak>Into Twilight</unbreak>
140903.Desc: <u>Summons memosprite</u> Little Ica, restores HP equal to <color=#f29e38ff><unbreak>#1[f1]%</unbreak></color> of Hyacine's Max HP plus <color=#f29e38ff><unbreak>#2[i]</unbreak></color> for all allies aside from Little Ica, and restores HP equal to <color=#f29e38ff><unbreak>#6[f1]%</unbreak></color> of Hyacine's Max HP plus <color=#f29e38ff><unbreak>#7[i]</unbreak></color> for Little Ica. Hyacine enters the "After Rain" state for <unbreak>#5[i]</unbreak> turn(s) afterward. Reduces the state's duration by 1 turn each time Hyacine's turn begins. When in "After Rain" state, increases Max HP for all allies by <color=#f29e38ff><unbreak>#3[f1]%</unbreak></color> plus <color=#f29e38ff><unbreak>#4[i]</unbreak></color>.

140904.Name: First Light Heals the World
140904.Desc: The memosprite Little Ica initially has Max HP equal to <unbreak>#1[i]%</unbreak> of Hyacine's Max HP. When Hyacine or Little Ica provides healing, increases Little Ica's DMG dealt by <color=#f29e38ff><unbreak>#3[i]%</unbreak></color> for <unbreak>#4[i]</unbreak> turn(s). Stacks up to <unbreak>#5[i]</unbreak> time(s).

140906.Name: Attack
140906.Desc: Attacks an enemy, and when the battle starts, reduces their Toughness of the corresponding Type.

140907.Name: Day So Right, Life So Fine!
140907.Desc: At the start of the next battle, restores HP equal to <unbreak>#1[i]%</unbreak> of Hyacine's Max HP plus <unbreak>#2[i]</unbreak> for all allies and increases their Max HP by <unbreak>#3[i]%</unbreak> for <unbreak>#4[i]</unbreak> turn(s).

1.PointDesc: Increases Hyacine and Little Ica's CRIT Rate by <unbreak>#1[i]%</unbreak>. When providing healing to an ally target with less than or equal to <unbreak>#2[i]%</unbreak> this unit's Max HP, increases Hyacine and Little Ica's Outgoing Healing by <unbreak>#3[i]%</unbreak>.
Increases Hyacine's Effect RES by <unbreak>#1[i]%</unbreak>. When using Skill and Ultimate, dispels <unbreak>#2[i]</unbreak> <u>debuff(s)</u> from all ally targets.

When Hyacine's SPD exceeds <unbreak>#1[i]</unbreak>, increases her and Little Ica's Max HP by <unbreak>#2[i]%</unbreak>. Then, for every <unbreak>#3[i]</unbreak> excess SPD, increases Hyacine's and Little Ica's Outgoing Healing by <unbreak>#4[i]%</unbreak>. Up to a max of <unbreak>#5[i]</unbreak> excess SPD can be taken into account for this effect.

1140901.Name: Rainclouds, Time to Go!
1140901.Desc: Deals Wind DMG to all enemies equal to <color=#f29e38ff><unbreak>#1[i]%</unbreak></color> of the tally of healing done by Hyacine and Little Ica in the current battle, and clears <unbreak>#2[i]%</unbreak> of the tally of healing.

1140903.Name: Take Sky in Hand
1140903.Desc: Little Ica's SPD remains at 0, is immune to <u>debuffs</u>, and they will not appear on the Action Order.\nIf ally targets (except Little Ica) have their HP reduced, then Little Ica will consume HP equal to <unbreak>#1[i]%</unbreak> of their own Max HP and restore HP equal to <color=#f29e38ff><unbreak>#2[f1]%</unbreak></color> of Hyacine's Max HP plus <color=#f29e38ff><unbreak>#3[i]</unbreak></color> for the ally target with reduced HP at the start of any target's turn or after any target takes action.\nWhile Hyacine is in the "After Rain" state, Little Ica immediately obtains 1 <u>extra turn</u> and automatically uses "Rainclouds, Time to Go!" after Hyacine uses an ability. Moreover, when Little Ica triggers their Talent's healing effect, additionally restores HP for all ally targets by an amount equal to <color=#f29e38ff><unbreak>#4[f1]%</unbreak></color> of Hyacine's Max HP plus <color=#f29e38ff><unbreak>#5[i]</unbreak></color>. After Little Ica uses an ability, all <u>Continuous Effects</u>' duration decreases by 1 turn.

1140905.Name: Soar, Unto the Sunlight
1140905.Desc: When summoned, additionally regenerates <unbreak>#1[i]</unbreak> Energy for Hyacine. When first summoned, additionally regenerates <unbreak>#2[i]</unbreak> Energy.

1140906.Name: Fall, Then Take Wing
1140906.Desc: Upon disappearing, advances the action of Hyacine by <unbreak>#1[i]%</unbreak>.
